text = "[center][b][color=#dd8f61]PyQuest[/color][/b]
[i]Learn Programming Through Adventure[/i][/center]
[center]──────────────────────────────[/center]
[b][color=#dd8f61]ABOUT THE PROJECT[/color][/b]
PyQuest is a thesis final project that aims to teach programming concepts through gamification. Each concept or lesson is divided into levels, using Python as the foundation.
[center]──────────────────────────────[/center]
[b][color=#dd8f61]HOW IT WORKS[/color][/b]
[b]01 — Pick a Level[/b]
Each level focuses on one core Python concept, from variables and loops to functions and data structures.
[b]02 — Play Through It[/b]
Solve challenges and puzzles designed around that concept. Learning happens through doing.
[b]03 — Level Up[/b]
Complete the level to unlock the next concept and watch your Python skills grow.
[center]──────────────────────────────[/center]
[b][color=#dd8f61]THE TEAM[/color][/b]
[b]X[/b] — Researcher, Game Developer
[b]Y[/b] — Researcher
[b]Z[/b] — Researcher
[center]──────────────────────────────[/center]
[b][color=#dd8f61]TOOLS & TECHNOLOGIES[/color][/b]
[b]Aseprite[/b] — Pixel art and animation editor
[b]Godot Engine[/b] — Game engine
[b]FastAPI[/b] — Python web framework
[b]Visual Studio Code[/b] — Code editor
[b]Git[/b] — Version control
[b]GitHub[/b] — Repository hosting
[center]──────────────────────────────[/center]
[b][color=#dd8f61]ATTRIBUTIONS[/color][/b]
The following third-party assets were used in the development of PyQuest. Full credit goes to their respective creators.

[b]Treasure Hunters[/b] by Pixel Frog
Primary asset pack used throughout the game.
[url=https://pixelfrog-assets.itch.io/treasure-hunters]pixelfrog-assets.itch.io/treasure-hunters[/url]

[b]Bringer of Death[/b] by Clembod
Used as the Level 20 boss character.
[url=https://clembod.itch.io/bringer-of-death-free]clembod.itch.io/bringer-of-death-free[/url]

[b]Mecha Golem[/b] by DarkPixel-Kronovi
Used as a level 10 boss in the game.
[url=https://darkpixel-kronovi.itch.io/mecha-golem-free]darkpixel-kronovi.itch.io/mecha-golem-free[/url]

[b]Slime Sprite 32x32[/b] by Vimlark
Used as an enemy character asset.
[url=https://vimlark.itch.io/slime-sprite-32x32]vimlark.itch.io/slime-sprite-32x32[/url]
[center]──────────────────────────────[/center]
"

